 illustrates the subtle distinction between semimetals and semiconductors\nin correlated electron systems. This distinction is relevant to investigations\nof correlated topological insulators and semimetals.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 31 Aug 2022 04:47:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 26 Sep 2022 02:56:08 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 15 Mar 2023 05:31:38 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 13 Apr 2023 02:14:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-14"}
