courses, and the relationship between the density and\ntemperature indicates that the heating is mainly caused by adiabatic\ncompression.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 31 Aug 2022 09:37:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-14"}
