 charm mixing is attributed to the strong\nGlashow-Iliopoulos-Maiani suppression on perturbative contributions, instead of\nto breakdown of the quark-hadron duality, which occurs only at 15\\% level.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 31 Aug 2022 12:24:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 8 Mar 2023 05:32:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-29"}
