 $N_{\\rm H_2} \\simeq 1.1$ and $1.4\\times10^{21}\\,$cm$^{-2}$,\nrespectively, consistent with the results of previous studies. Our results\nconfirm the existence of a coupling between magnetic fields at cloud scales and\nfilaments at smaller scale. They also illustrate the potential of combining\nHerschel and Planck observations, and they call for further statistical\nanalyses with our dedicated method.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 31 Aug 2022 13:19:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-14"}
